CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 20, 1946, pg. 29 reads: "Wedding Celebration - A reception honoring Mr. and Mrs. Cornelius Patterson was held at Carney Post last week following the ceremony which united the couple at Homewood AME Zion Church. The bride is the former Miss Marian Arrington, daughter of Samuel C. Arrington of Torrens Street, and the groom is the son of Mrs. Martha L. Patterson of Susquehanna Street. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Full length group portrait of men and women, including bride Marian Arrington Patterson and groom Cornelius Patterson, cutting four tiered wedding cake, gathered behind long banquet table in Carney Post for wedding reception, another version
